                                       -----------------------------------
                                       Diamond 2 Plasma Theme Changelog
                                       -----------------------------------

Diamond v. 2.0.3 (27/08/2014)
- KDE 4.14 compatible
- Fix problem panels solid black
                                       
Diamond v. 2.0.2 (01/08/2014)
- Fix close button in dialog shown in the corners active
- Improvements in the contrasts of the various elements of the theme
- Add new effects in the task

Diamond v. 2.0.1 (7/05/2014)
- KDE 4.13 compatible
- Add volume icon monochrome
- Improved notification icon
- Improved mini-calendar icon
- Other fix

Diamond v. 2.0 (31/12/2013)
- KDE 4.11 and KDE 4.10 compatible
- Revised the various elements of the theme
- Added documentation
- Added new widget clock
- Revised buttons colors
- Improved contrast
- Better color in scrollbars for usability
- Improved notification icon
- Added mini-calendar icon
- Other fix

 


                                        
                                        
                               
















                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       *_v1.3 Jan 04 2013

-KDE 4.10.x compatible
-Updated documentation (and added SourceForge site)
-Added desktop notification icon
-New widgets arrows
-Fixed a bug in "viewitem" (thanks to Hyslion for the fix)
-Added toolbar-icons
-Added mini-calendar icon
-Revised Quassel icon
-New printer icon
-New accessibility (text to speech) icon
-New ethernet connection icon
-Added presence applet for Telepathy KDE
-Added new mail icons
-New configuration icons
-Added weather icons (ready for compabitily)
-New Konversation icon
-Revised buttons colors
-Removed display widget
-Added experimental wallpaper/pattern

